            <p style="margin-right: 10px; letter-spacing: 1px; color: white; transform: translate(3px, -296px); text-align: justify; left: 6%; position: absolute; width: 29%;">Originally from a small town in the south of Italy Angelo Accardi moved to Napoli to study fine arts at the Art Academy of Naples. Shortly after, in the early 90s, he set up his personal studio close to his childhood home to embark on his pursuit of painting and sculpture. In the course of his artistic development, Accardi has been on a constant search for new sensations using mixed media to depict figures against differing social backgrounds.</p>
