            <p style="margin-right: 10px; letter-spacing: 1px; color: white; transform: translate(3px, -754px); text-align: justify; left: 63%; position: absolute; width: 34%;">Born and raised in Munich, Metis Atash is German by nationality but considers herself a global citizen. After successfully operating her own investor relations consultancy boutique, Metis channeled her devotion and passion for art, design, and fashion into the creation of one-of-a-kind sculptures. It was on the Indonesian island of Bali where she discovered the lifestyle, culture, and philosophies that most strongly resonated with her. Eventually, this became the inspiration and trajectory for both her artistic style and her purpose as an artist.</p>

